none; display: block; background-position: -3284px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #4a7194; position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 4px; top: 4px;\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/press_review/2013/02/130228_press_china_korea_ana.shtml\">中共党校学者：中国应该放弃朝鲜</a></li>\n<li class=\"ts-headline body-disabled teaser\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-image: none; display: block; background-position: -3284px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #4a7194; position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 4px; top: 4px;\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2013/02/130220_nkorea_nuclear.shtml\">韩媒：朝鲜数周内无法再度核试验</a></li>\n<li class=\"ts-headline body-disabled teaser\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-image: none; display: block; background-position: -3284px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #4a7194; position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 4px; top: 4px;\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2013/02/130219_china_north_korea.shtml\">英媒：朝核试爆冲击力 中国感受最苦涩</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"more-contextual-links\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; font-size: 12px;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #4a7194; position: relative; display: inline-block;\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/press_review/2013/04/130401_china_scholar_korea.shtml#more-contextual-links\">更多相关的故事</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"list li-relatedtopics\" style=\"font-size: 1em; float: none; margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; clear: right; width: 224px;\">\n<h2 class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-size: 16px; color: #505050; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 20px; position: relative; top: 0px; overflow: hidden; border-style: solid none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: #cccccc; border-bottom-color: #cccccc; height: 20px;\">相关新闻话题</h2>\n<div class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 1em; padding-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; overflow: hidden;\">\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">\n<li class=\"primary-topic\" style=\"margin: 0px 4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: none; display: block; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-position: -3284px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a class=\"topic\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #4a7194; position: relative; display: inline;\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/topics/china\">中国</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">邓聿文在文章中说，中国最佳的选择是采取主动权，争取朝鲜半岛的统一。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">在接受《朝鲜日报》的电话采访时，邓聿文称中国外交部就他这篇文章向中共党校兴师问罪。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">电话采访引述邓聿文的话说，由于这篇文章他（副编审）的职务&ldquo;已被解除&rdquo;，他被&ldquo;无限期停职，不过仍在领取薪水，不知何时才会被给予另一个职位&rdquo;。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">《纽约时报》在报道这一消息时称，他们周一（4月1日）同邓聿文联系，但邓聿文拒绝就此给予评论。</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 8px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; color: #505050; line-height: 24px; position: relative; top: 0px; overflow: hidden; border: none; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">邓聿文观点</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">中共党校学者邓聿文在给英国《金融时报》撰写的文章中说，朝鲜的第三次核试验对中国来说是一个重新审视它与金氏王朝长期盟友关系的最佳时刻。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">邓聿文指出，中国那种基于地缘政治而与朝鲜建立起来的战略盟友关系已经过时了。此外，一种靠建立在意识形态上的关系是很危险的。虽然中国和朝鲜都是社会主义国家，但两国之间的区别甚至大于中国和西方社会。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">邓聿文还在文章中说，朝鲜一旦有了核武器，不能排除反复无常的金氏王朝以核武来要挟中国&#8230;&#8230;基于上述考虑，中国应该放弃朝鲜，而最好的解决办法就是斡旋朝鲜半岛的统一。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">《纽约时报》的报道评论道，由于邓聿文中共党校《学习时报》副编审的地位，这篇文章发表后引起了华盛顿及欧洲的多方关注，一些人将此解读为北京新领导对朝鲜感到厌烦，准备调整对平壤的政策。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">不过，到目前为止，没有任何迹象显示，中国政策制定者会响应邓聿文文章中提出的建议。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; font-family: arial, 'Heiti SC', 宋体, helvetica, verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/press_review/2013/04/130401_china_scholar_korea.shtml\">原文链接</a></p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,8779],"tags":[13088,8843]}